tags.name: lrn-table
tags.description:
`lrn-table`
`Accessibly render a HTML table from a csv file`

Attributes:

  * `title` {`string`} - Title of this table. This is both for accessibility and presentation.

  * `csv-file` {`string`} - The file to load material from.

  * `description` {`string`} - An extended description of the material in the table for improved accessibility.

  * `schemaMap` - Schema Map for the element, used to generate a valid prefix on the fly
Props set for Polymer compatibility
